{"tid":2109121,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"咸蝦菜：多國抗疫走錯方向","createTime":"2020-07-15T04:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T05:12:29.000Z","uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c847fd95f8a4706cf4c92bd386fe6e3f18afdcd1","tid":2109121,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎全球大流行約半年，但世界衞生組織（WHO，簡稱世衞）總幹事譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）聲言，很多國家在抗疫工作方面仍然「走往錯誤方向」，又形容新型冠狀病毒依然是頭號公敵。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>譚德塞警告，太多國家領袖在應對疫情時，發出混亂信息及未有採取正確的抗疫措施；但他未明言哪些國家做得不好。</strong><br />\n<br />\n譚德塞指，大眾需要認真採取保持社交距離、勤洗手、佩戴口罩等措施，又警告或難以在可見的將來回復「舊常態」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，如果不做好以上的基本措施，疫情只會變得愈來愈嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n世衞指美洲國家 現密集式傳播<br />\n<br />\n世衞公共衞生緊急計劃執行主任瑞安（Mike Ryan）則表示，部分美洲國家放寬封鎖措施，令部分地區出現「密集式傳播」（intense transmission）。<br />\n<br />\n拉丁美洲共錄得逾14.5萬宗新冠肺炎死亡個案，近半是來自巴西。巴西總統博索納羅（Jair Bolsonaro）一直抗拒採取嚴厲措施，以防止病毒擴散。<br />\n<br />\n瑞安承認，大範圍封城措施將會帶來重大經濟後果，但在特定地區實行以避免病毒擴散，仍是有其必要性。他敦促各國政府制定清晰而有力的策略，讓大眾更能夠理解，更容易遵從配合。<br />\n<br />\n瑞安重申，大眾需要學習在病毒威脅下生活，任何預期病毒可以在數月內消滅，或疫苗在數月內面世，都是不切實際。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：張志堂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://paper.hket.com/article/2695784/%E8%AD%9A%E5%BE%B7%E5%A1%9E%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E3%80%8C%E8%B5%B0%E5%BE%80%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E3%80%8D?dis=pd&amp;pdlist=srap001&amp;mtc=70024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2695784%2F%25E8%25AD%259A%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%25A1%259E%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%25BE%2580%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2590%2591%25E3%2580%258D%3Fdis%3Dpd%26pdlist%3Dsrap001%26mtc%3D70024&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5GuwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=23c83d8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://paper.hket.com/article/2695784/%E8%AD%9A%E5%BE%B7%E5%A1%9E%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E3%80%8C%E8%B5%B0%E5%BE%80%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E3%80%8D?dis=pd&amp;pdlist=srap001&amp;mtc=70024</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7448b29bcd74245463aab5f909fc1f81edf4a94","tid":2109121,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:15:08.000Z","msg":"對，要同支國合作"},{"pid":"8986b66dffeb29ca4c24ea4a93d48d335b6eb000","tid":2109121,"uid":82267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:16:04.000Z","msg":"一早咁講 <br />\n個病短期內都冇得搞<br />\n你要個國家停落黎幾耐？<br />\n人民生活要停幾耐？<br />\n一定要如常生活架喇"},{"pid":"0b39fb75f5d86c2265450cde247bc13fa00019b1","tid":2109121,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbe2dfbe8de9894e916c86a1f8a381c92e283c53","tid":2109121,"uid":46943,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"有一個國家做得好<br />\n不過政治不正確所以唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e72e357db98ac24d73174627f65c6851347d6e","tid":2109121,"uid":177955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:31:18.000Z","msg":"多得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053ccef5ed914902fcb85e8d56f9b16e2b1dbe7e","tid":2109121,"uid":275692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:36:53.000Z","msg":"係佢最初叫其他國家唔好封關同無需要戴口罩"},{"pid":"6a509e8898fa60fe3862ac62d8f06c358b7e7fbf","tid":2109121,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"053ccef5ed914902fcb85e8d56f9b16e2b1dbe7e","tid":2109121,"uid":275692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:36:53.000Z","msg":"係佢最初叫其他國家唔好封關同無需要戴口罩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\